    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/96877f54a820b4661745c0781beb8466.poster.avif?t=1646673914\" width=616 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/96877f54a820b4661745c0781beb8466.webm?t=1646673914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/96877f54a820b4661745c0781beb8466.mp4?t=1646673914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>《主播与地牢》</strong>是一款免费DLC，它将<strong>Twitch</strong>与<strong>Mixer</strong>集成到<strong>《恶魔之书》</strong>。当您在玩游戏的时候，您的观看者将通过聊天窗疯狂输入指令。除了给您派来怪物和设下陷阱，他们也会在挑战过程中帮助您。他们究竟会帮助还是祸害您呢？碰碰运气，看看能否在纸做的地牢中智胜他们吧！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/020b661b2c55722f56ba7e056dd4141a.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> 允许您的<strong>Twitch</strong>或者<strong>Mixer</strong>观看者与您的游戏进行互动<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/020b661b2c55722f56ba7e056dd4141a.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> 启用或禁用所选功能<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/020b661b2c55722f56ba7e056dd4141a.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> 控制观看者的互动程度 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/020b661b2c55722f56ba7e056dd4141a.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> 限制付费订阅者的互动（Twitch）<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>互动类型</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/4059987d96a89c0de7445b7af3f35ee5.poster.avif?t=1646673914\" width=616 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/4059987d96a89c0de7445b7af3f35ee5.webm?t=1646673914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/4059987d96a89c0de7445b7af3f35ee5.mp4?t=1646673914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏过程中，屏幕下方的指令条显示观看者可以发出的指令。在地牢中，常有6种基本互动方式（其中包括3种良性互动、3种负面互动），加上两种特殊互动。您的观看者可通过在聊天窗输入指令激活此功能。例如，<i>+heal</i>。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>基本互动</strong></h2>每一种基本互动都有其激活概率百分比，在互动名称后面的括号里显示。这是观看者的指令可以真正被执行的概率。如果很多人发出相同的指令，将降低被激活的概率；相反，如果发出鲜有人发出的指令，被激活的概率将增加。如果很多人发出相同的指令，直到被激活的概率直降为0%，该指令则会变成冷却状态。<br><br><br><strong>良性：</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/6beca454216f4051800db9d240fc550b.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <i>+heal</i> – 在玩家周围投放生命或法力水晶<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/6beca454216f4051800db9d240fc550b.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <i>+hit</i> – 给玩家周围的随机怪物造成伤害<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/6beca454216f4051800db9d240fc550b.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <i>+drop</i> – 在玩家周围随机投放奖励（金币、卡牌充能等）<br><br><strong>负面：</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/6a9543e95229a7cbe6ef7d32a223f804.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <i>-spawn</i> – 在玩家周围随机投放一个怪物<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/6a9543e95229a7cbe6ef7d32a223f804.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <i>-card</i> – 给玩家的卡牌造成负面效果（冲撞、蛛网套住等）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/6a9543e95229a7cbe6ef7d32a223f804.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <i>-steal</i> – 随机摧毁一个可见奖励<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特殊互动</strong></h2><br>特殊互动效果更强大，其表现也有所不同。一开始，它们在冷却状态。一旦变成可使用状态，则只能激活一次，或者在指定时间内可激活。之后，它们被其它随机的特殊指令所取代。 <br><br><strong>良性：</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/6beca454216f4051800db9d240fc550b.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <i>+prize</i> – 在玩家周围随机投放奖励 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/6beca454216f4051800db9d240fc550b.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <i>+throw</i> – 当被激活，观看者可以输入 <i>+throw</i> 从玩家周围击退随机怪物<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/6beca454216f4051800db9d240fc550b.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <i>+godmode</i> – 短时间内，神圣护盾保护玩家<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/6beca454216f4051800db9d240fc550b.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <i>+stun</i> – 当被激活，观看者可输入 <i>+stun</i> 击晕怪物<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/6beca454216f4051800db9d240fc550b.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <i>+deathrage</i> – 激活玩家的死亡愤怒效果<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/6beca454216f4051800db9d240fc550b.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <i>+freeze</i> – 当被激活，观看者可输入 <i>+freeze</i> 冻结随机怪物<br><br><strong>负面：</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/6a9543e95229a7cbe6ef7d32a223f804.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <i>-stun</i> – 击晕玩家<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/6a9543e95229a7cbe6ef7d32a223f804.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <i>-poison</i> – 使玩家中毒<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/6a9543e95229a7cbe6ef7d32a223f804.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <i>-boss</i> – 在玩家周围随机投放一个BOSS<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/6a9543e95229a7cbe6ef7d32a223f804.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <i>-freeze</i> – 冻结玩家<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/6a9543e95229a7cbe6ef7d32a223f804.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <i>-burn</i> – 在玩家脚下放火<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/6a9543e95229a7cbe6ef7d32a223f804.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <i>-icetrap</i> – 使玩家被冰柱包围<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/6a9543e95229a7cbe6ef7d32a223f804.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <i>-mouse</i> – 当被激活，观看者可输入 <i>-mouse</i> 冲撞玩家的鼠标光标<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/6a9543e95229a7cbe6ef7d32a223f804.webp?t=1646673914\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <i>-throw</i> – 当被激活，观看者可输入 <i>-throw</i> 向玩家投掷怪物<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>传奇卡牌投票</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/8b09a5d897373b519a93e4ada277a695.poster.avif?t=1646673914\" width=616 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/8b09a5d897373b519a93e4ada277a695.webm?t=1646673914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/8b09a5d897373b519a93e4ada277a695.mp4?t=1646673914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>当您找到一张魔法卡牌，您需要把它带到智者那里鉴定。如果是一张传奇卡牌（最稀有的卡牌种类），您将有两张不同卡牌可供您的观看者选择。投票期间，您的观看者必须输入 <i>+vote1</i> 或 <i>+vote2</i>。每一个人只能投票一次。如果投票结果平局，将随机选择卡牌。 <br><br>您可以在选项栏关闭此功能，或者设置投票时长（默认为30秒）。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>连接方法</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/59be3ae3a75da08ccdb80e7c97113701.poster.avif?t=1646673914\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/59be3ae3a75da08ccdb80e7c97113701.webm?t=1646673914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968890/extras/59be3ae3a75da08ccdb80e7c97113701.mp4?t=1646673914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在您能够与您的观看者开始游戏前，首先您需要把<strong>《恶魔之书》</strong>连接到您的Twitch或Mixer帐户。当您安装完毕DLC，在人物选择画面的右下角将显示一个新按钮。点击可查看<strong>《主播与地牢》</strong>的连接与配置窗口。<br><br>在左侧可设置与Twitch或Mixer的连接。为此，您需要输入您的频道名称，并申请一个OAuth令牌（Twitch）或者从外部浏览器登录Mixer。在Twitch模式，您还可以限制您的付费频道订阅者的互动。 <br><br>在右侧，您可以调整集成选项。将鼠标放在复选框标签，查看每一项功能的解释。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>观看者互动选项</strong></h2><br>您可以在观看者互动滑块调整您的观看者影响游戏的程度。将此项调低可使您的游戏保持稳定，但同时您的观看者威胁或帮助您的机会也会较低。如果调高则会变成完全任由您的观看者摆布，且他们的指令将决定游戏的难度。 <br><br><i><strong>提醒：</strong> 观看者互动程度也被该频道观看者的活跃人数所影响，因此拥有更多活跃的观看者并不会使游戏失去稳定。 </i>",
